HTML Elements:

Skeleton:

<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <title>HTML Skeleton</title>
    <link href="styles/main.css" rel="stylesheet" type="text/css">
  </head>
  <body>
    <header>
      <!-- Header content -->
    </header>
    <!-- Content -->

    <script src="https://code.jquery.com/jquery-3.2.1.min.js"></script>
    <script src="scripts/app.js"></script>
  </body>
</html>

Basic elements:
<a href = “link”> Link! </a>
<a href = “link” target = “_blank” > New Window link! </a>
<img src=”link” alt=”description”>

Passing template vars to front end JS:

<script>
    window.tournamentID = <%=tournamentID%>;
</script>

